                        <del rend="strikethrough">Command</del>] <gloss target="#t_CINCUNC1"
                            >CINCUNC</gloss> to increase [<del rend="strikethrough"
                            >immediately</del>] the scale of military operations in the Korean [<del
                            rend="strikethrough">campaign</del>
                        <del rend="strikethrough">to</del>
                        <del rend="strikethrough">the</del>
                        <del rend="strikethrough">maximum</del>] <hi rend="italic">area</hi>
                        consistent with the capabilities [<del rend="strikethrough">and</del>
                        <del rend="strikethrough">security</del>] of the forces [<del
