                        <del rend="strikethrough">North</del>
                        <del rend="strikethrough">Korean</del>
                        <del rend="strikethrough">Peninsula</del>];</p>
                    <p>(4) …</p>
                    <p>(5) …</p>
                    <p>(6) …</p>
                    <p>(7) Remove all restrictions against air attacks <hi rend="italic">in North
