                        <del rend="strikethrough">border</del>];</p>
                    <p>(8) Take the necessary [<del rend="strikethrough">UN</del>
                        <del rend="strikethrough">and</del>] diplomatic measures <hi rend="italic"
                            >for</hi> [<del rend="strikethrough">looking</del>
                        <del rend="strikethrough">toward</del>] the imposition of <hi rend="italic"
                            >a naval and</hi> an economic blockade of Communist China [<del
                            rend="strikethrough">and</del>
                        <del rend="strikethrough">re-examine</del>
                        <del rend="strikethrough">the</del>
                        <del rend="strikethrough">political</del>
