                        <del rend="strikethrough">above</del>
                        <del rend="strikethrough">wording</del>
                        <del rend="strikethrough">is</del>
                        <del rend="strikethrough">a</del>
                        <del rend="strikethrough">State</del>
                        <del rend="strikethrough">Department</del>
                        <del rend="strikethrough">proposal</del>
                        <del rend="strikethrough">.)</del>];</p>
                    <p>(9) …</p>
                    <p>
                        <hi rend="italic">b</hi>.…</p>
                    <p>Add the following new paragraph under 2<hi rend="italic">a</hi>:</p>
                    <p>“Employ U.S. Air Forces unilaterally and on short notice if the situation so
                        requires to attack certain Chinese communist air bases whenever the scale of
                        these activities is such as to seriously jeopardize the security of the U.S.
                        forces in the Korean area.”</p>
